data.name: Dawn Wings Necrozma-GX
rules: Pokémon-GX rule: When your Pokémon-GX is Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.

abilities.name: Invasion
abilities.text: Once during your turn (before your attack), if this Pokémon is on your Bench, you may switch it with your Active Pokémon.

attacks.name: Dark Flash
attacks.text: This attack's damage isn't affected by Resistance.

attacks.name: Moon's Eclipse-GX
attacks.text: You can use this attack only if you have more Prize cards remaining than your opponent. Prevent all effects of attacks, including damage, done to this Pokémon during your opponent's next turn. (You can't use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)

data.name: Necrozma-GX
rules: Pokémon-GX rule: When your Pokémon-GX is Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.

abilities.name: Light's End
abilities.text: Prevent all damage done to this Pokémon by attacks from Colorless Pokémon.

attacks.name: Prismatic Burst
attacks.text: Discard all Psychic Energy from this Pokémon. This attack does 60 more damage for each card you discarded in this way.

attacks.name: Black Ray-GX
attacks.text: This attack does 100 damage to each of your opponent's Pokémon-GX and Pokémon-EX. This damage isn't affected by Weakness or Resistance. (You can't use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)

data.name: Necrozma

attacks.name: Barrier Attack
attacks.text: During your opponent's next turn, this Pokémon takes 30 less damage from attacks (after applying Weakness and Resistance).

attacks.name: Special Laser
attacks.text: If this Pokémon has any Special Energy attached to it, this attack does 60 more damage.

data.flavorText: It looks somehow pained as it rages around in search of light, which serves as its energy. It's apparently from another world.

data.name: Dawn Wings Necrozma

attacks.name: Gulf Stream
attacks.text: If you have exactly 6 Prize cards remaining, this attack does 20 more damage for each damage counter on this Pokémon.

attacks.name: Sword of Dawn
attacks.text: Discard 2 Energy from this Pokémon.

data.flavorText: Lunala no longer has a will of its own. Now under the control of Necrozma, it continuously expels all of its energy.

data.name: Dusk Mane Necrozma

attacks.name: Dusk Shot
attacks.text: This attack does 60 damage to 1 of your opponent's Pokémon-GX or Pokémon-EX. This damage isn't affected by Weakness or Resistance.

attacks.name: Rusty Claws
attacks.text: If your opponent has exactly 1 Prize card remaining, this attack does 100 more damage.

data.flavorText: This is its form with it is devouring the light of Solgaleo. It pounces on its foes and then slashes them with the claws on its four limbs and back.
